 Yusuf, the son of President Muhammadu Buhari, is planning to marry the daughter of Emir of Bichi in Kano State, Nasir Bayero Zahra Bayero is currently a student in the United Kingdom, studying architecture. Yusuf is a 2016 graduate of the University of Surrey, Guildford, United Kingdom. Credible sources told DailyNigerian that the wedding ceremony would take place “in the next two to three months”. “Preparations are on top gear for the grand event. As the tradition provides, the parents of the groom have met with the parents of the bride to express Yusuf’s interest in marrying Zahra,” the source said, pleading anonymity.